The '''sting-brush''' was a type of [[Plant/Legends|plant]] native to the arid [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Kamar/Legends|Kamar]]. Like many other plants, sting-brushes were relatively fragile, but they extruded a substance that could irritate the skin of most organic life-forms. Sting-brushes depended upon this feature to avoid being consumed by predators.

